'''Pandhiyâng''' (''Zingiber cassumunar'') iyâ arèya sala sèttong tombuwân palappa. Tombuwân arèya andi' nyama cem-macem, misalla: ''mungle'' (Aceh), ''bungle'' (Tapanuli), ''kunik bolai'' (Minang), ''banglee'iy'' (Rejang), ''panglai'' (Sunda), ''bale'' (Makassar), ''panini'' (Bugis), bân ''unin makei'' (Ambon).

